          "pageScope": true,
          "script": "\tsystem.perspective.print(\"IN DefectsEditPanel\")\n\tsystem.perspective.print(\"Payload received is: %s\"%payload)\n\t\n\tself.getChild(\"cntColumn\").getChild(\"cntDefectLevel1\").getChild(\"txt\").props.text \u003d payload[\u0027DefectCategory\u0027]\n\tself.getChild(\"cntColumn\").getChild(\"cntDefectLevel2\").getChild(\"txt\").props.text \u003d payload[\u0027DefectName\u0027]\n\tself.getChild(\"cntColumn\").getChild(\"cntUnitName\").getChild(\"txt\").props.text\u003dpayload[\u0027DefectSubName\u0027]\n\tself.getChild(\"cntColumn\").getChild(\"cntDemerit\").getChild(\"txt\").props.text\u003dpayload[\u0027Demerit\u0027]\n\t\n\tsystem.perspective.print(\"SYtem: %s\"%payload[\u0027Defect_Id\u0027])  \n\tsystem.perspective.print(payload[\u0027DefectName_Id\u0027])\n\tsystem.perspective.print(payload[\u0027DefectSUBName_Id\u0027])\n\t\n\tself.custom.DefectCategoryId \u003d payload[\u0027Defect_Id\u0027]\n\tself.custom.DefectNameId \u003d payload[\u0027DefectName_Id\u0027]\n\tself.custom.DefectSubnameId \u003d payload[\u0027DefectSUBName_Id\u0027]\n\t\n\tself.custom.payload \u003d payload\n\t\n\n\t",
